data.description: View the virtual tour of this pristine & secluded 4 bed 3 bath brick home sitting on 2 acres. The basement features separate living quarters with separate den, kitchen and 2 beds & 1 bath. 2 car garage on Main Level and carport for Basement, RV Storage, Workshop, Whole House Generac, Whole House Water Filter, Security Camera System, & Sunroom overlooking the expansive backyard fully fenced in. The spacious master ensuite features dual vanities with granite countertop, separate shower, & walk-in closet. The living room flows into the dining room and kitchen, creating a perfect space for entertaining. Kitchen features granite & butcher block countertops. 10 minutes from Guntersville
